{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Vicca Afiliados Page",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "bg_color",
      "label": "Background Color",
      "default": "#fdf9f3"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Vicca Afiliados Page"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<section class="vap-page" style="background-color: {{ section.settings.bg_color }};">

  {%- comment -%} HERO {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="vap-hero">
    <div class="vap-container">
      <p class="vap-hero-pretitle">vicca<span class="vap-dot">.</span>agency</p>
      <h1 class="vap-hero-title">
        <span class="vap-serif">Programa de</span>
        <span class="vap-bold">afiliados</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="vap-hero-desc">Conviértete en un <strong>vicca<span class="vap-dot">.</span>afiliate</strong> y ayuda a personas a empezar una nueva vida en Holanda con nuestro programa, <strong>ganando dinero por ello.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} WHAT IS IT {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="vap-section">
    <div class="vap-container">
      <h2 class="vap-section-title">Ser un vicca<span class="vap-dot">.</span>afiliate es...</h2>
      <div class="vap-cards-row">
        <div class="vap-info-card">
          <span class="vap-card-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>Recomendar un programa que <strong>acompaña de verdad</strong> a las personas que quieren mudarse a Holanda.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vap-info-card">
          <span class="vap-card-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>Conectar a personas que lo necesitan con un programa <strong>honesto y bien estructurado.</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="vap-info-card">
          <span class="vap-card-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>Si esa persona entra en Step Into Opportunity, tú recibes una <strong>comisión por tu recomendación.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} TARGET + REQUIREMENTS — side by side cards {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="vap-section vap-section-alt">
    <div class="vap-container vap-container-wide">
      <div class="vap-dual-grid">

        <div class="vap-dual-card">
          <div class="vap-dual-label">Para ti si...</div>
          <h2 class="vap-dual-title">¿A quién va dirigido?</h2>
          <p class="vap-dual-sub">Este programa está pensado para personas que:</p>
          <div class="vap-dual-list">
            <div class="vap-dual-item">
              <span class="vap-dual-icon">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Creen en hacer las cosas bien, <strong>sin atajos</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="vap-dual-item">
              <span class="vap-dual-icon">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Valoran el <strong>acompañamiento real</strong> frente a las promesas vacías</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vap-dual-item">
              <span class="vap-dual-icon">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Recomiendan desde la <strong>honestidad</strong>, no desde la presión</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vap-dual-item">
              <span class="vap-dual-icon">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Prefieren construir <strong>confianza</strong> antes que volumen</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="vap-dual-footer">Queremos pocos afiliados, pero alineados.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vap-dual-card vap-dual-card-dark">
          <div class="vap-dual-label vap-dual-label-light">Requisitos</div>
          <h2 class="vap-dual-title">Ser vicca<span class="vap-dot">.</span>afiliate</h2>
          <p class="vap-dual-sub">No pedimos números, pedimos actitud.</p>
          <div class="vap-dual-list">
            <div class="vap-dual-item">
              <span class="vap-dual-icon vap-dual-icon-dark">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Comunicación <strong>honesta y clara</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="vap-dual-item">
              <span class="vap-dual-icon vap-dual-icon-dark">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Recomendar solo a personas que <strong>realmente encajen</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="vap-dual-item">
              <span class="vap-dual-icon vap-dual-icon-dark">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Respetar el <strong>proceso y las normas</strong> del programa</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vap-dual-item">
              <span class="vap-dual-icon vap-dual-icon-dark">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Valorar el <strong>trato cercano y humano</strong></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="vap-dual-footer">Si esto te suena lógico, probablemente encajes.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} HOW IT WORKS {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="vap-section vap-section-alt">
    <div class="vap-container">
      <h2 class="vap-section-title">Conviértete así...</h2>
      <div class="vap-steps">
        <div class="vap-step">
          <div class="vap-step-number">1</div>
          <h3 class="vap-step-title">Regístrate</h3>
          <p>Completa el formulario con tu nombre y tu email pulsando el botón de abajo.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vap-step">
          <div class="vap-step-number">2</div>
          <h3 class="vap-step-title">Recibe la información completa</h3>
          <p>Te enviaremos por email todos los detalles del programa de afiliados: funcionamiento, condiciones, comisiones y forma de pago.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vap-step">
          <div class="vap-step-number">3</div>
          <h3 class="vap-step-title">Confirma y empieza</h3>
          <p>Si todo encaja contigo, nos lo confirmas y quedas registrado/a oficialmente como vicca<span class="vap-dot">.</span>afiliate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} BENEFITS {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="vap-section">
    <div class="vap-container">
      <h2 class="vap-section-title">¿Qué te llevas como vicca<span class="vap-dot">.</span>afiliate?</h2>
      <div class="vap-benefits">
        <div class="vap-benefit">
          <span class="vap-benefit-icon">&#128176;</span>
          <p>Comisiones por cada persona que contrate Step Into Opportunity gracias a tu recomendación</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vap-benefit">
          <span class="vap-benefit-icon">&#128196;</span>
          <p>Un sistema claro y sin letra pequeña</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vap-benefit">
          <span class="vap-benefit-icon">&#128172;</span>
          <p>Comunicación directa con el equipo vicca<span class="vap-dot">.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="vap-benefit">
          <span class="vap-benefit-icon">&#127793;</span>
          <p>Formar parte de un proyecto en crecimiento, con valores claros</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} CTA BUTTONS {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="vap-cta-section">
    <div class="vap-container">
      <p class="vap-cta-text"><strong>Si te identificas con esta forma de hacer las cosas</strong> y quieres recibir toda la información en detalle sin compromiso...</p>
      <div class="vap-cta-buttons">
        <button type="button" class="vap-btn vap-btn-orange" onclick="viccaOpenSignupModal()">Quiero afiliarme</button>
        <button type="button" class="vap-btn vap-btn-black" onclick="viccaOpenAffiliateModal()">Ya soy vicca.afiliate</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  .vap-page {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    color: #000;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .vap-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .vap-dot { color: #ff914d; font-weight: 900; }

  /* HERO */
  .vap-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 20px 80px;
  }

  .vap-hero-pretitle {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    color: #000;
  }

  .vap-hero-title {
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    line-height: 0.9;
  }

  .vap-serif {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 400;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .vap-bold {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 80px);
    font-weight: 900;
    display: block;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  .vap-hero-desc {
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #333;
  }

  /* SECTIONS */
  .vap-section {
    padding: 70px 20px;
  }

  .vap-section-alt {
    background: rgba(255, 145, 77, 0.04);
  }

  .vap-section-title {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 34px);
    font-weight: 800;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .vap-section-sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .vap-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #555;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  /* CARDS ROW */
  .vap-cards-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .vap-info-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vap-card-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #ff914d;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .vap-info-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* DUAL CARDS */
  .vap-container-wide {
    max-width: 1100px;
  }

  .vap-dual-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .vap-dual-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 32px;
    padding: 40px 36px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  .vap-dual-card-dark {
    background: #111;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .vap-dual-label {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #ff914d;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .vap-dual-label-light {
    color: #ff914d;
  }

  .vap-dual-title {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.5vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .vap-dual-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .vap-dual-list {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .vap-dual-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .vap-dual-card:not(.vap-dual-card-dark) .vap-dual-item {
    color: #333;
  }

  .vap-dual-card-dark .vap-dual-item {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  }

  .vap-dual-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #ff914d;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .vap-dual-icon-dark {
    background: #ff914d;
    color: #111;
  }

  .vap-dual-footer {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .vap-dual-card-dark .vap-dual-footer {
    border-top-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    color: #ff914d;
  }

  /* STEPS */
  .vap-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .vap-step {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 8px;
  }

  .vap-step-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #000;
    color: #ff914d;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .vap-step-title {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .vap-step p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #555;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* BENEFITS */
  .vap-benefits {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .vap-benefit {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .vap-benefit-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .vap-benefit p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* CTA SECTION */
  .vap-cta-section {
    padding: 80px 20px 100px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vap-cta-text {
    font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    color: #000;
  }

  .vap-cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .vap-btn {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: 0.3s ease;
    padding: 18px 44px;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .vap-btn-orange {
    background: #ff914d;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .vap-btn-orange:hover { background: #e87a3a; }

  .vap-btn-black {
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .vap-btn-black:hover { background: #222; }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .vap-hero { padding: 70px 20px 60px; }
    .vap-section { padding: 50px 16px; }
    .vap-cards-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .vap-dual-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .vap-dual-card { padding: 32px 24px; border-radius: 24px; }
    .vap-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .vap-benefits { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .vap-cta-section { padding: 60px 16px 80px; }

    .vap-cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 340px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .vap-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 16px 32px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .vap-hero { padding: 56px 16px 48px; }
    .vap-bold { letter-spacing: -1px; }
    .vap-section { padding: 40px 12px; }
    .vap-section-title { font-size: 22px; }
    .vap-section-sub { font-size: 15px; }
    .vap-check-item { font-size: 14px; }
    .vap-step-title { font-size: 16px; }
    .vap-info-card { padding: 24px 18px; border-radius: 18px; }
    .vap-dual-card { padding: 28px 20px; border-radius: 20px; }
    .vap-dual-title { font-size: 20px; }
    .vap-dual-item { font-size: 14px; }
    .vap-benefit { padding: 22px 18px; border-radius: 16px; }
    .vap-cta-section { padding: 48px 12px 70px; }
    .vap-cta-text { font-size: 16px; }
    .vap-highlight { font-size: 15px; }
  }
</style>
